dump: U-= Trenton A. Breazeale =--= So on I worked and waited for my light.        =--= Not knowing, I settled into my bed;            =--= That Trenton Breazeale, one calm winter night, =--= Went home and put a bullet through his head.   =--= September 10, 1980 - February 22, 1998 =--= R.I.P. Good Buddy.  You will never be forgotten. =-Please Help Somebody Today.Tomorrow may be too late.Tomorrow was too late to help Trent...
